com.appboy.ui.actions

Class GooglePlayAppDetailsAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appboy.ui.actions.GooglePlayAppDetailsAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAction

    public final class GooglePlayAppDetailsAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAction
    Action that opens the Google Play market to a specific app in either the Google Play store app or via the AppboyWebViewActivity class. If it is opened in the AppboyWebViewActivity class, the time spent viewing the app in the web view counts toward the session duration.
